rows.label: bf10240150_0010
rows.name:
When people lose something,
they inevitably search for a reason why.

rows.label: bf10240150_0020
rows.name: They look within themselves and within others...

rows.label: bf10240150_0030
rows.name: They want someone to define it for them.

rows.label: bf10240150_0040
rows.name: The fundamental question of who they truly are.

rows.label: bf10240150_0060
rows.name:
Yet perhaps that very loneliness
is what defines humanity.
